@node CFGR_CC "ARexx configration 'Cancel'"
@toc CFGR

ARexx configuration 'Cancel'
----------------------------

When  you're  done but don't want to keep the changes click in the 'Cancel'
gadget. The changes will be discarded and the old settings will be used.

